明清时期的官服在前襟后背各缀有一块补子，称为“补服”，也称“补褂”。补服比袍短，类似于褂，又比褂略长，其袖端平，对襟，所以又名“外褂”。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.diybuyi.com/2259.html|title = 明清各级官员补服、补子|accessdate = 2015-07-14|author = 纨素|date = 2015-04-11|publisher = |deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150714093231/http://www.diybuyi.com/2259.html|archivedate = 2015-07-14|df = }}</ref><gallery>
